title: S16 Ep111: Strange Stories of Aliens, Angels, and God from The Bible w/Jason Malott
itunes:title: Strange Stories of Aliens, Angels, and God from The Bible w/Jason Malott
description:
Darkness Radio presents Strange Stories of Aliens, Angels, and God from The Bible with Jason Malott

Dave & Tim have a fun, funny and insightful conversation with author/researcher Jason Malott about the stories of the Bible and the many misdirections of supernatural influence in it's pages.  What do these stories tell us about our beliefs, ourselves and the world?  We examine Angels, Aliens and other mysterious encounters in a fast paced, evocative and entertaining discussion aimed at making you think and taking you along on a journey.

Get the book here: https://amzn.to/3lolXZe
